lead_paragraph: LEAD: The Market Place column in Business Day on Dec. 15 about a method for turning ''junk bonds'' into investment-grade securities misstated the status of a regulatory review of the First Executive Corporation's attempt to repackage some bonds. The California Department of Insurance is conducting an examination of the transaction and has not yet reached a decision on it.
